title: Case Keenum trade, OBJ Rumors, FA Preview with Ryan Wilson/John Breech (Football 3/8)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson and John Breech to break down a crazy day in the NFL. First up, Brinson and Breech talk about the Case Keenum trade from the Broncos to the Redskins (1:00), then Wilson joins in to discuss the Odell Beckham rumors (11:45) and some Josh Rosen/Kyler Murray talk. Finally the guys preview the upcoming NFL free agency period (26:00).
